title: Serhant on NY Real Estate, New Season of "Owning Manhattan"
description:
Ryan Serhant, SERHANT CEO, says New York City doesn’t have enough rental supply to meet demand. He tells Romaine Bostick and Katie Greifeld on “The Close” that prices are high not because of market forces but because of policy.
 (Source: Bloomberg)
